01:06:24.500 --> 01:06:26.240
And then playing
back sound files.

01:06:26.240 --> 01:06:31.180
So at certain times, I tried to
improvise everything, and write

01:06:31.180 --> 01:06:32.620
software to
improvise everything.

01:06:32.620 --> 01:06:35.260
And I've sort of moved
