01:07:17.440 --> 01:07:18.940
help with the
brainstorming of this.

01:07:18.940 --> 01:07:21.490
But one of the things
that does come to mind

01:07:21.490 --> 01:07:27.540
is do the sounds you record
suggest any kind of structure?

01:07:27.540 --> 01:07:31.230
So, for example, if you're
thinking locker room,

01:07:31.230 --> 01:07:35.614
if I go to the gym, I
