01:07:35.614 --> 01:07:37.030
I don't how much
noise that makes.

01:07:37.030 --> 01:07:38.155
It's probably pretty quiet.

01:07:38.155 --> 01:07:40.182
But the bang of the lockers.

01:07:40.182 --> 01:07:42.140
What do you do with the
